These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Sport: volleyball, cycling, golf
1. Sport:cycling is on the right of Sport:golf##1
2. Sport:volleyball is on the far right##1
3. Sport:volleyball is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | golf | cycling | volleyball |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Food: pepper, cauliflower, grapes
1. Food:cauliflower is in an odd position##4
2. Food:pepper is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | pepper | grapes | cauliflower |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Hobby: singing, camping, video-games
1. Hobby:camping is in an even position##4
2. Hobby:camping is on the left or right of Hobby:video-games##3
3. Hobby:video-games is on the right of Hobby:camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | singing | camping | video-games |

 #################################
 
